---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Catálogo"
  description="Catálogo de productos Grupo METRO — Bebidas, refrescos, cervezas, aguas, licores y más. Precios actualizados Junio 2026."
>

<!-- ═══════ HERO CATÁLOGO ═══════ -->
<section class="hero-bg pt-20 pb-12 sm:pt-28 sm:pb-16 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="absolute top-10 right-10 w-60 h-60 rounded-full bg-amber-400/3 blur-3xl"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center relative z-10">
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-amber-400/10 border border-amber-400/20 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 mb-6">
      <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-amber-400"></span>
      <span class="text-amber-400 text-xs tracking-wider uppercase font-medium">Junio 2026</span>
    </div>
    <h1 class="font-display text-5xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl leading-[0.95]">CATÁLOGO</h1>
    <p class="text-zinc-400 mt-4 sm:mt-5 max-w-lg mx-auto text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">
      Consulta todos nuestros productos, formatos y precios actualizados. Nuevas referencias cada mes.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════ PDF + VISTA PREVIA ═══════ -->
<section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-black relative">
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-px section-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-5 gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Texto -->
      <div class="md:col-span-3">
        <span class="text-amber-400 text-xs sm:text-sm tracking-[.3em] uppercase">Descarga</span>
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl text-amber-400 mt-3 mb-5 leading-[1.05]">CATÁLOGO<br>COMPLETO</h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-base leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-lg">
          Nuestro catálogo incluye todos los productos disponibles con sus precios actualizados (IVA incluido).
          Ábrelo en una pestaña nueva o descárgalo para consultarlo cuando quieras.
        </p>

        <!-- Botones -->
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
          <a
            href="/catalogo-junio-2026.pdf"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="group bg-amber-400 text-black px-8 py-4 font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-sm text-center hover:bg-amber-300 transition-all duration-200"
          >
            <span class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
              📄 Abrir Catálogo PDF
              <span class="inline-block transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-0.5" aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
            </span>
          </a>
          <a
            href="/catalogo-junio-2026.pdf"
            download
            class="group border border-zinc-700 bg-zinc-900/50 px-8 py-4 text-sm tracking-wider uppercase text-center hover:border-amber-400/50 transition-all duration-200"
          >
            <span class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-zinc-300 group-hover:text-amber-400 transition-colors">
              ⬇ Descargar PDF
            </span>
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Info extra -->
        <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-xs text-zinc-600">
          <span>📄 47 páginas</span>
          <span>💶 Precios + IVA</span>
          <span>📅 Actualizado Junio 2026</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Visual -->
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-amber-400/5 rounded-2xl blur-2xl" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="relative bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
            <div class="bg-zinc-800/50 px-4 py-3 border-b border-zinc-800 flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500/60"></span>
              <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-amber-400/60"></span>
              <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500/60"></span>
              <span class="text-xs text-zinc-500 ml-2 font-mono">catalogo-junio-2026.pdf</span>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <img
                src="/logo.jpg"
                alt="Grupo METRO — Catálogo Junio 2026"
                class="w-full max-w-[200px] mx-auto rounded-lg mb-4"
                loading="lazy"
                width="200" height="100"
              />
              <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm font-semibold text-center">Catálogo Junio 2026</p>
              <p class="text-zinc-600 text-xs text-center mt-1">Formato PDF · 47 páginas · Precios + IVA</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════ CATEGORÍAS ═══════ -->
<section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-zinc-950 relative">
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-px section-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <span class="text-amber-400 text-xs sm:text-sm tracking-[.3em] uppercase">Productos</span>
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl mt-3 mb-4 leading-[1.05]">¿QUÉ ENCONTRARÁS?</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm sm:text-base max-w-lg mx-auto">Cuatro grandes categorías con las marcas más demandadas por hostelería y retail.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 sm:gap-6">
      <!-- Refrescos -->
      <div class="group bg-zinc-900/60 border border-zinc-800/80 rounded-xl p-6 sm:p-8 text-center hover:border-amber-400/40 transition-all duration-300 card-lift">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-5 rounded-xl bg-zinc-800/50 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-amber-400/5 transition-colors">
          <img src="/logos/Coca-Cola.svg" alt="" class="h-12 w-auto object-contain" loading="lazy" aria-hidden="true" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-white text-sm sm:text-base mb-2">Refrescos</h3>
        <p class="text-zinc-500 text-xs leading-relaxed">Coca-Cola, Fanta, Nestea, Don Simon, Granini, Juver, Viladrau</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Aguas -->
      <div class="group bg-zinc-900/60 border border-zinc-800/80 rounded-xl p-6 sm:p-8 text-center hover:border-amber-400/40 transition-all duration-300 card-lift">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-5 rounded-xl bg-zinc-800/50 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-amber-400/5 transition-colors">
          <img src="/logos/Evian.svg" alt="" class="h-12 w-auto object-contain" loading="lazy" aria-hidden="true" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-white text-sm sm:text-base mb-2">Aguas</h3>
        <p class="text-zinc-500 text-xs leading-relaxed">Font Vella, Evian, Bezoya, Nestlé, Solán de Cabras, Perrier, San Pellegrino</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Cervezas -->
      <div class="group bg-zinc-900/60 border border-zinc-800/80 rounded-xl p-6 sm:p-8 text-center hover:border-amber-400/40 transition-all duration-300 card-lift">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-5 rounded-xl bg-zinc-800/50 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-amber-400/5 transition-colors">
          <img src="/logos/Heineken.svg" alt="" class="h-12 w-auto object-contain" loading="lazy" aria-hidden="true" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-white text-sm sm:text-base mb-2">Cervezas</h3>
        <p class="text-zinc-500 text-xs leading-relaxed">Estrella Damm, Heineken, Mahou, San Miguel, Corona, Budweiser, Guinness</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Energéticas + Licores -->
      <div class="group bg-zinc-900/60 border border-zinc-800/80 rounded-xl p-6 sm:p-8 text-center hover:border-amber-400/40 transition-all duration-300 card-lift">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-5 rounded-xl bg-zinc-800/50 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-amber-400/5 transition-colors">
          <img src="/logos/Red-Bull.svg" alt="" class="h-12 w-auto object-contain" loading="lazy" aria-hidden="true" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-white text-sm sm:text-base mb-2">Energéticas + Licores</h3>
        <p class="text-zinc-500 text-xs leading-relaxed">Red Bull, Powerking, Brugal, Larios, DYC, Kopparberg, Strongbow</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════ CÓMO PEDIR ═══════ -->
<section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-black relative">
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-px section-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="absolute bottom-10 right-10 w-40 h-40 rounded-full bg-green-500/3 blur-3xl"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center relative z-10">
    <span class="text-amber-400 text-xs sm:text-sm tracking-[.3em] uppercase">Pedidos</span>
    <h2 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl text-amber-400 mt-3 mb-5 leading-[1.05]">¿CÓMO PEDIR?</h2>
    <p class="text-zinc-400 text-base max-w-lg mx-auto mb-8 leading-relaxed">
      Contacta con nosotros por WhatsApp y te preparamos el pedido. Sin aplicaciones, sin registros, sin esperas.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-10 text-left">
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/60 border border-zinc-800/80 rounded-xl p-5 flex items-start gap-3">
        <span class="w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-amber-400 text-black flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold shrink-0 mt-0.5">1</span>
        <div>
          <p class="text-white text-sm font-semibold">Escríbenos</p>
          <p class="text-zinc-500 text-xs mt-0.5">Cuéntanos qué productos necesitas y cantidades.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/60 border border-zinc-800/80 rounded-xl p-5 flex items-start gap-3">
        <span class="w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-amber-400 text-black flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold shrink-0 mt-0.5">2</span>
        <div>
          <p class="text-white text-sm font-semibold">Presupuesto</p>
          <p class="text-zinc-500 text-xs mt-0.5">Te confirmamos precios y disponibilidad al momento.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/60 border border-zinc-800/80 rounded-xl p-5 flex items-start gap-3">
        <span class="w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-amber-400 text-black flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold shrink-0 mt-0.5">3</span>
        <div>
          <p class="text-white text-sm font-semibold">Entrega</p>
          <p class="text-zinc-500 text-xs mt-0.5">Recíbelo en tu negocio. Rápido y sin complicaciones.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a
      href="https://wa.me/34600781881"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-green-600 text-white px-10 py-5 font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-sm hover:bg-green-500 transition-all duration-200 pulse-ring"
    >
      <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/></svg>
      Pedir por WhatsApp
    </a>
    <p class="text-zinc-600 text-xs mt-4">+34 600 781 881 · Respuesta rápida garantizada</p>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
